            <h6 class="kicker"><span class="kicker-label"><a href="http://www.nytimes.com/pages/opinion/index.html">The Opinion Pages</a></span><span class="pipe">|</span>Foreign Wars and Terrorism</h6>
        </div><!-- close story-meta -->
